      "rationale": "All five flow-speed operating points were tested on the FDA generic pump test rig. Inlet flow rate (±1.5%), rotational speed (±10 RPM), and fluid temperature (±0.5°C) were recorded and match CFD boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty. Gradation 2 is achieved."
