    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Class II device at medium model influence. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index agree with bench-test measurements within uncertainty bounds across all five operating points. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied for all worst-case conditions. The credibility evidence package is accepted to support the regulatory submission.",
